responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "68C625534EA948C1B72E3A8ABFEB40AE", "Quite the contrary, friend. The Forsaken Blade have intercepted an extra large shipment of healing supplies headed for Halcyon. This time, they\'ve really gone out of their way to make a mess of things. Without those vital reserves, we\'re going to be at our lowest point yet. We need to break in and recover those supplies without giving them any warning signs of our preparations. And quickly.")
